      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯称以色列杀死了其政治领导人，此举加剧了该地区的紧张局势，导致油价出现自四月份以来的最大涨幅。该地区原油产量占全球原油总产量的三分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 23:29:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
